code: public static Stat getStatistics(Message message) {     Stat stats = null.     if (message != null) {         stats = message.getHeader(ZOOKEEPER_STATISTICS, Stat.class).     }     return stats. }
public static String getPath(Message message) {     String path = null.     if (message != null) {         path = message.getHeader(ZOOKEEPER_NODE, String.class).     }     return path. }
@Override public DefaultMessage newInstance() {     return new ZooKeeperMessage(getCamelContext()). }
